ution": "Andaman Isls, Australia, Borneo, China, India, Indochina, Java, Lesser Sunda Isls, Malay Peninsula, Moluccas, Myanmar, New Guinea, Philippines, Sri Lanka, Sulawesi, Thailand. BABUYAN ISLS, CAGAYAN DE SULU, LUZON: Batangas, Ilocos Norte, La Union, Laguna, NCR, Pangasinan, Rizal, Zambales (photos), MINDANAO: Zamboanga, PALAWAN, QUEZON ISL, SULU ARCHIPELAGO, UBIAN.", "notes": "Throughout the Philippines; dry lowland or coastal thickets, bound to seasonal climatic conditions. Deciduous when fruiting. Sea level and lowland.", "conservation_status": "Least Concern (IUCN 3.1).", "dao_category": "", "other_fields": {}, "gallery_url": "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/cgi-bin/bhbase/cubic_gallery_public.pl?start_at=0&taxon_name=Capparis+sepiaria", "thumbs": ["http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/paraman1/3_11_08_2/SA11Mar08Hor2/1230CapparisSepiaria.JPG.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/paraman1/3_11_08_2/SA11Mar08Hor2/1231CapparisSepiaria.JPG.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/7_4_15/4Jul15/DSC_8206.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/7_4_15/4Jul15/DSC_8200.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/7_4_15/4Jul15/DSC_8202.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/7_4_15/4Jul15/DSC_8203.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/7_4_15/4Jul15/DSC_8198.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/7_4_15/4Jul15/DSC_8196.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/7_4_15/4Jul15/DSC_8204.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/7_4_15/4Jul15/DSC_8199.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGES/phytoimages/pelserpb/7_4_15/4Jul15/DSC_8197.jpg.400.jpg", "http://herbarium.bh.cornell.edu/CUBIC_IMAGE